{"tid":438130,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲翻舊公司做","createTime":"2017-10-16T15:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T17:29:40.000Z","uid":35501,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9e43649d6f02bf4ece96d98c8d6d45be26218f94","tid":438130,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:23:11.000Z","msg":"最近比人炒左，年尾又搵唔到工<br />\n咁岩舊公司請人，我就打比舊同事R撈<br />\n當初都算好黎好去，老細都有話歡迎我翻去做<br />\n咁當然係門面說話啦<br />\n如果我真係翻去做，會唔會好尷尬<br />\n有無巴打分享下"},{"pid":"283eded51d64f1a7c615f128580597e916fe82d8","tid":438130,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:52:42.000Z","msg":"個個掩住半邊咀笑你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你頂得順咪得囉！"},{"pid":"68882e4bf4e74a7709760b0a96723880261b7579","tid":438130,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T16:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返囉，但係你問下自己當初點解會走先，再睇返宜家接唔接受到"},{"pid":"efd055a19d020cdd4cdb1b7dd5d9c4a5cbcf269d","tid":438130,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T16:15:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5da52096bbe04c2d563ed1519a7aa9096ccb3b5d","tid":438130,"uid":124838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T16:18:43.000Z","msg":"好馬不吃回頭草啊ching"},{"pid":"ecf95c0c37986ae23f51009eb2b14faa4421dfbd","tid":438130,"uid":7644,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T16:19:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好馬不吃回頭草啊ching</blockquote><br />\n好草不怕回頭吃啊Ching"},{"pid":"b2a5d1dbd648955965f253dfe91ff248cf17c962","tid":438130,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:28:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個掩住半邊咀笑你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你頂得順咪得囉！</blockquote><br />\n但真係搵唔到工，唔通食谷種咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802735489ac167fa3c89be6a011171d320d3c482","tid":438130,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:29:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>笑死 又要威又要返來</blockquote><br />\n我都咁覺得<br />\n走啦，當初走唔係好得戚好威嫁咩，宜家撈唔掂又翻黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8682489b4ca47d652a56db8aad89813f7644de9","tid":438130,"uid":74497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:31:43.000Z","msg":"人工有冇加到先<br />\n有咪型,冇咪柒"},{"pid":"1da17de0a9d6cb1aed9ad6417085d99237a61d6a","tid":438130,"uid":35501,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:39:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人工有冇加到先<br />\n有咪型,冇咪柒</blockquote><br />\n有呀，多過我走之前，多過我比人炒個份<br />\n但title無變"},{"pid":"a21d32b5d827d41b7e0ff4717bf478e4daca18e7","tid":438130,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T05:38:23.000Z","msg":"我公司都有好幾個同事都係咁返黎<br />\n<br />\n其實之前走既原因係咩"},{"pid":"06f9f787b57676f72272616e2ab29a37b79dbe03","tid":438130,"uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T05:42:09.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n之前走咗 新工番咗5個月 唔啱做辭咗工<br />\n<br />\n舊上司問我番唔番去做<br />\n公司賣咗盤 要我番去做執個邊<br />\n<br />\n人工又高咗 又hea"},{"pid":"5dc4fb0e1e6970cbd43772dd4ef75db13838a170","tid":438130,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T05:54:04.000Z","msg":"唔會介意背後俾人笑咪返囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見識過有個好厚面皮既舊同事<br />\n果陣夏天，臨走四圍同人講出去裝冷氣人工高一截<br />\n冬天果陣就話唔捨得呢個大家庭，但據聞人工比走之前低左"},{"pid":"3f5952078427454dd8fbb6a43811489afb6f0759","tid":438130,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T06:31:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我公司都有好幾個同事都係咁返黎<br />\n<br />\n其實之前走既原因係咩</blockquote><br />\n之前走係因為覺得行頭太窄，怕自己做多幾年到30，但呢份工既經驗對我搵其他工無幫助<br />\n但其實老細同事都好人，就算我走呢大半年都keep住同同事食飯唱k玩"},{"pid":"498d6a3a41f525e4fa7f1b536a773a0ec11fac02","tid":438130,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T06:32:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會介意背後俾人笑咪返囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見識過有個好厚面皮既舊同事<br />\n果陣夏天，臨走四圍同人講出去裝冷氣人工高一截<br />\n冬天果陣就話唔捨得呢個大家庭，但據聞人工比走之前低左</blockquote><br />\n我就係驚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我走個時又無四圍講乜講乜咁衰仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3362717e7c6565f2b1e96b501750361638610d","tid":438130,"uid":22557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T08:25:56.000Z","msg":"唉<br />\n我都轉左新公司差唔多2個月<br />\nfeel到依間公司好唔掂, structure 氣氛啊<br />\n不停有人走同請人<br />\n不過唔會返舊公司, 好尷尬"},{"pid":"b9620d9c0c26e7b79d6077de3638e02da58b2f0e","tid":438130,"uid":106930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T17:24:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好馬不吃回頭草啊ching</blockquote><br />\n好草不怕回頭吃啊Ching</blockquote><br />\n好草當初就咪走啦Ching"},{"pid":"3485c660f2e4f719d0f7bea3116cc251e828a73f","tid":438130,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T17:25:34.000Z","msg":"錢多左咪得囉<br />\n<br />\n理撚得咁多咩"},{"pid":"5ddc6b36ac84364e842a1d1919e08a5899d8d237","tid":438130,"uid":49461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T17:28:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好馬不吃回頭草啊ching</blockquote><br />\n好草不怕回頭吃啊Ching</blockquote><br />\n好草當初就咪走啦Ching</blockquote><br />\n駁唔到"},{"pid":"800e8a9bee385c480eb5bac882b9feeab4ee2840","tid":438130,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T17:29:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好馬不吃回頭草啊ching</blockquote><br />\n好草不怕回頭吃啊Ching</blockquote><br />\n好草當初就咪走啦Ching</blockquote><br />\n駁唔到</blockquote><br />\n魚唔過塘點肥呀CHING"}]}